/#
   The credit rating notation higher level construct, which provides the ability to specify multiple rating notations.
 #/
record FpML5.legal.CreditNotations {
  # The 'all' signifies that all of the specified credit notations are applicable; equivalent to a logical 'and' expression.
  creditNotation : FpML5.legal.CreditNotation

  # An enumerated element, to qualify whether All or Any credit notation applies.
  condition : string

}

creditNotation.Doc: The 'all' signifies that all of the specified credit notations are applicable; equivalent to a logical 'and' expression.
creditNotation.Name: creditNotation

condition.Doc: An enumerated element, to qualify whether All or Any credit notation applies.
condition.Name: condition
